13:13.279 --> 13:14.221
Thank you, Smokey.

13:15.402 --> 13:25.175
Friends, you know it's your own state forestry department along with the United States Forest Service and this station you're listening to that makes these little outdoor get-togethers possible.

13:25.936 --> 13:29.881
